SUMMARY:Essays on Industrial Organization and Consumer Behavior
DTSTAMP:20260630T134717Z
DTSTART:20260710T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:&#160\;  Speaker: Ruosi Li  Doctoral Candidate  Thesis Defense 
	 Department: Economics  Location: Kraft Hall Kraft 402\;&#160\;  My disser
	tation contains two chapters\, and they are all about consumer demand esti
	mation when consumers do not have a perfect understanding of the products 
	they are buying. The first chapter is about consumer confusion\, and the s
	econd one is about limited consideration.  Zoom link: https://riceuniversi
	ty.zoom.us/j/2460173918?pwd=d1p1NjN0ekwvclVXdkgybUQ0VXcxdz09&amp\;omn=9439
	8956547  (Department : Economics)\n\nhttps://events.rice.edu/live/events/4
