	 by an adult \n\n\n\nDid you know that you can make fresh cheese and butte
	r easily in your own kitchen? Join us to learn how to make queso fresco-st
	yle cheese and home-“churned” butter! We’ll explore a little cooking chemi
	stry and experiment with adding flavors from herbs and spices. \n\n\n\nPle
	ase dress for the weather and wear clothes you don’t mind getting messy. \
	n\n\n\n\nRegister Online\n\nhttps://houstonarboretum.org/event/diy-dairy/\
	n\nFrom Houston Arboretum & Nature Center
